reqs.description:
The data science minor, along with a suitable major, will prepare students for graduate level study and entry level positions in data science and data analysis.
Students will develop competency in:
Programming in a computer language used in data science work. Currently this means the ability to work in Python and/or R;
Statistical thinking and mathematical modeling;
The use of machine learning software tools;
Data management and the overall data science process, through project experience.
